    <item>
      <title>美联社称哈里斯已获得足够票数赢得总统提名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/harris-crosses-delegate-threshold-in-sign-nomination-is-hers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过为期两天的激烈竞选，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 已获得足够多的承诺代表票数，足以获得民主党总统候选人提名。此次竞选为她巩固了党内支持，让她能够在 11 月挑战唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/harris-crosses-delegate-threshold-in-sign-nomination-is-hers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:47:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党公布提名规则，哈里斯势头强劲 举行虚拟投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/democrats-unveil-nomination-rules-virtual-vote-as-harris-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党提议在提名过程中采用虚拟投票，并设定最低代表门槛以进行投票——这概述了竞选规则，随着副总统卡马拉·哈里斯（Kamala Harris）的退出，这场竞选可能很快就会变得毫无意义。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/democrats-unveil-nomination-rules-virtual-vote-as-harris-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 23:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1MDB 逃犯 Low 必须交出母亲的三颗“完美无瑕”钻石</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/1mdb-fugitive-low-must-forfeit-mom-s-trio-of-flawless-diamonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刘特佐 (Low Taek Jho) 被控策划了马来西亚 1MDB 基金的掠夺，他被勒令没收他为母亲购买的三颗“完美无瑕”的钻石，这些钻石来自一家曾为碧昂斯和阿黛尔等名人设计的珠宝商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/1mdb-fugitive-low-must-forfeit-mom-s-trio-of-flawless-diamonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 23:11:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
