      <title>拜登议程“全速推进”，官员们前往亚洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-agenda-full-steam-ahead-with-officials-traveling-to-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们表示，尽管拜登总统决定不再寻求连任，但他的高级外交和国防官员本周仍按计划访问日本和菲律宾，这是他“全速前进”对待世界其他地区政策的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-agenda-full-steam-ahead-with-officials-traveling-to-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 21:29:30 GMT</pubDate>
